@NODE MAIN "GXTeam"
     Name         : GXTeam

     Aliases      : No Aliases

     Type/Size    : Boot/1024

     Clones       : No Clones 

     Symptoms     : No Symptoms

     Discovered   : 10-06-90

     Way to infect: Boot infection

     Rating       : Harmless

     Kickstarts   : 1.2

     Damage       : Overwrites boot.

     Removal      : Install boot.

     Comments     : If you are booting with a GXTEAM-Virus infected
                    disk the virus copies itself to $7F4D0. To infect
                    other disks the virus patches the DoIO()-Vector.
                    Additionally the virus changes the KICK & Cool-Vec.
                    to stay resdient in memory. Finally the virus
                    patches $6C (ZERO-PAGE). If a value reaches 4432
                    the virus decrypts a text to address $7F300 and
                    gives out an (french) alert.
                    You can`t read the text in the bootblock because
                    it is crypted.

                    Click on the gadget to see a @{" Demo " SYSTEM V-IFF:GXTeam} of the GXTeam
                    virus. Push left mouse button to return.

